Are you with us or not?

278
00:25:18.013 --> 00:25:19.471
Sweet Pea, take break.

279
00:25:20.181 --> 00:25:21.433
Yeah.

280
00:25:28.943 --> 00:25:30.277
Babydoll.

281
00:25:31.321 --> 00:25:32.989
Come over here.

282
00:25:33.615 --> 00:25:34.866
Come, come.

283
00:25:40.332 --> 00:25:42.167
