317
00:29:26.155 --> 00:29:27.196
You guess?

318
00:29:28.325 --> 00:29:29.783
No, I...

319
00:29:30.952 --> 00:29:32.454
I know.

320
00:29:34.290 --> 00:29:35.540
I need to get out of here.

321
00:29:35.708 --> 00:29:37.710
Freedom.

322
00:29:37.878 --> 00:29:39.295
That wasn't so hard, was it?

323
00:29:40.130 --> 00:29:43.133
I'm going to help you to be free.

324
00:29:43.301 --> 00:29:44.510
What do I have to do?

325
00:29:48.307 --> 00:29:51.060
WISE MAN:
These are your weapons.

326
00:29:55.107 --> 00:29:57.443
When you take them,
