327
00:29:58.278 --> 00:30:00.529
Your journey to freedom.

328
00:30:14.632 --> 00:30:17.843
You will need five items for this journey.

329
00:30:18.011 --> 00:30:20.304
The first is a map.

330
00:30:20.472 --> 00:30:23.392
Then fire, a knife and a key.

331
00:30:24.352 --> 00:30:26.104
You said five things.

332
00:30:26.271 --> 00:30:28.940
The fifth thing is a mystery.

333
00:30:29.192 --> 00:30:32.569
It is the reason. It is the goal.

334
00:30:33.531 --> 00:30:37.618
It will be a deep sacrifice
and a perfect victory.

335
00:30:40.872 --> 00:30:45.127
Only you can find it.

336
00:30:45.754 --> 00:30:47.380
And if you do...

337
00:30:48.924 --> 00:30:51.218
...it will set you free.

338
00:30:54.807 --> 00:30:57.183
