351
00:36:09.657 --> 00:36:11.033
That was crazy.

352
00:36:11.201 --> 00:36:14.788
ROCKET:
That was so amazing. I'm, like, shaking.

353
00:36:17.208 --> 00:36:20.461
ROCKET: I've never seen Madame Gorski
clap like that before.

354
00:36:20.629 --> 00:36:21.879
SWEET PEA:
Well, get over it.

355
00:36:22.047 --> 00:36:23.549
It's nearly lights out.

356
00:36:24.092 --> 00:36:25.926
She's not easily impressed.

357
00:36:26.094 --> 00:36:29.848
SWEET PEA: She wasn't impressed.
All that gyrating and moaning.

358
00:36:30.015 --> 00:36:32.935
The dance should be
more than just titillation.

359
00:36:33.103 --> 00:36:37.148
Mine's personal. It says who I am.

360
00:36:37.984 --> 00:36:39.610
What the heck does yours say?

361
00:36:39.778 --> 00:36:41.946
It says I'm gonna escape from here.

362
00:36:42.949 --> 00:36:44.157
That I'm gonna be free.

363
00:36:44.784 --> 00:36:47.370
Well, send me a postcard from paradise.

364
00:36:49.957 --> 00:36:51.834
Are you really gonna try to escape?

365
00:36:52.460 --> 00:36:55.171
Yeah. Before the High Roller comes.

366
00:36:55.339 --> 00:36:57.507
- Can I come?
- Me too.

367
00:36:59.678 --> 00:37:02.555
- Yeah, of course.
- You're not going anywhere, Rocket.

368
00:37:02.723 --> 00:37:04.224
I'm gonna do what I wanna do.

369
00:37:04.392 --> 00:37:07.770
No one's ever escaped from here.
You know that.

370
00:37:07.938 --> 00:37:10.857
Yeah. You know, the last three girls
that tried died.

371
00:37:11.526 --> 00:37:13.861
And the same thing'll happen
to the next fool.

372
00:37:14.029 --> 00:37:16.031
Look, why don't you just
listen to my plan?

373
00:37:16.198 --> 00:37:18.366
Don't wanna hear your plan, okay?

374
00:37:20.579 --> 00:37:22.496
None of us do.

375
00:37:37.767 --> 00:37:40.186
Now, let's get ready, girls.

376
00:37:40.354 --> 00:37:43.064
Rehearsal in 15 minutes.

377
00:38:05.551 --> 00:38:07.804
We're not helping Baby.

378
00:38:08.973 --> 00:38:11.474
- Am I clear?
- What if it's a good plan?

379
00:38:11.642 --> 00:38:14.395
Then she can go through with it.

380
00:38:14.688 --> 00:38:16.898
I'm not letting you get hurt.

381
00:38:17.817 --> 00:38:21.946
- I kept us safe through a lot of shit.
- I know you have.

382
00:38:22.447 --> 00:38:24.616
I'm not gonna get hurt.

383
00:38:25.785 --> 00:38:29.622
I just can't be here anymore.

384
00:38:29.790 --> 00:38:31.916
And if it is a good plan,
we're both going.

385
00:38:32.084 --> 00:38:34.294
No, we're not.

386
00:38:35.088 --> 00:38:36.923
You're on your own.

387
00:38:44.392 --> 00:38:45.726
[ROCKET SCOFFS]

388
00:38:51.567 --> 00:38:54.236
