00:38:54.404 --> 00:38:56.238
Sure you have.

390
00:38:57.199 --> 00:38:59.284
Look where that got us.

391
00:39:05.668 --> 00:39:07.002
[SIGHS]

392
00:39:07.795 --> 00:39:12.425
Baby saved me from the Cook
