and he gets on top of me...

396
00:39:25.276 --> 00:39:27.444
...and I can't even move.

397
00:39:28.529 --> 00:39:29.864
[SIGHS]

398
00:39:30.532 --> 00:39:33.035
And there she was, just like that.

399
00:39:34.037 --> 00:39:37.040
She had a knife to his throat.

400
00:39:38.042 --> 00:39:39.834
She saved me.

401
00:40:06.327 --> 00:40:08.870
The High Roller comes for me
in three days.

402
00:40:09.623 --> 00:40:11.958
But I'm getting out of here
before he does.

403
00:40:12.584 --> 00:40:16.046
So if you guys wanna come with me,
this is how I plan to do it.

404
00:40:22.180 --> 00:40:23.722
Well?

405
00:40:23.890 --> 00:40:25.266
Okay.

406
00:40:26.853 --> 00:40:30.815
If we can collect all four of these items,
we can be free.

407
00:40:30.983 --> 00:40:32.441
Okay.

408
00:40:32.609 --> 00:40:34.111
- How do we use them?
- Wait up.

409
00:40:34.988 --> 00:40:36.822
First things first.

410
00:40:36.990 --> 00:40:39.409
How do you plan on
getting these things?

411
00:40:39.577 --> 00:40:43.414
Well, whoever has the item we need,
we get them to watch me dance.

412
00:40:43.623 --> 00:40:46.209
While we run around
and pick their pockets?

413
00:40:46.377 --> 00:40:49.546
- Yeah, that's right.
- But we'd be taking all the risk.

414
00:40:49.714 --> 00:40:52.550
We'd be doing the work
while you prance around with an alibi.

415
00:40:52.718 --> 00:40:55.804
No. As long as I'm dancing,
they won't even know you're there.

416
00:40:55.972 --> 00:40:57.306
[SIGHS]

417
00:40:59.393 --> 00:41:02.313
Okay, so the first thing we need
is a map...

418
00:41:03.607 --> 00:41:06.943
...to figure out where all the exits are,
where the guards are located.

419
00:41:07.111 --> 00:41:09.905
Blue has that in his office.
It's behind his desk.

420
00:41:10.072 --> 00:41:11.365
Right. Good.

421
00:41:12.242 --> 00:41:14.494
Second thing we need
is something to start a fire with...

422
00:41:14.662 --> 00:41:16.997
