423
00:41:17.457 --> 00:41:19.792
<i>Plus, the fire should disable
all the checkpoints.</i>

424
00:41:20.794 --> 00:41:22.755
And the third thing is a knife...

425
00:41:23.423 --> 00:41:24.965
