426
00:41:25.634 --> 00:41:26.676
The Cook.

427
00:41:28.095 --> 00:41:30.555
- We can do it.
- Okay.

428
00:41:30.974 --> 00:41:32.475
And the last thing's a key.

429
00:41:33.894 --> 00:41:35.646
