439
00:42:04.975 --> 00:42:06.141
Me too.

440
00:42:07.645 --> 00:42:08.979
[SIGHS]

441
00:42:11.817 --> 00:42:12.942
All right.

442
00:42:14.361 --> 00:42:17.948
But I'm only doing this because you
guys'd get caught without me, okay?

443
00:42:18.116 --> 00:42:19.701
And if it gets too hairy...

444
00:42:21.036 --> 00:42:22.829
...if I say it's over...

445
00:42:22.997 --> 00:42:24.707
...we stop.

446
00:42:24.874 --> 00:42:26.417
Okay.

447
00:42:28.379 --> 00:42:29.504
Okay.

448
00:42:32.467 --> 00:42:33.551
I'll get the map.

449
00:42:38.933 --> 00:42:41.728
DANFORTH:
