481
00:46:52.1000 --> 00:46:57.212
So don't feel bad about killing them.

482
00:46:59.467 --> 00:47:01.051
They're already dead.

483
00:47:09.145 --> 00:47:10.520
Remember, ladies:

484
00:47:10.855 --> 00:47:12.607
If you don't stand for something...

485
00:47:13.525 --> 00:47:15.276
