486
00:47:16.613 --> 00:47:18.947
Oh, and one last thing:

487
00:47:20.951 --> 00:47:22.494
Try and work together.

488
00:47:38.973 --> 00:47:40.975
[WHISTLE BLOWING]

489
00:48:07.175 --> 00:48:08.969
[YELLING]

490
00:48:33.292 --> 00:48:34.709
Son of a...

491
00:49:49.929 --> 00:49:51.471
