01:35:24.375 --> 01:35:26.377
[GROANING]

871
01:35:32.718 --> 01:35:34.261
The second thing is...

872
01:35:37.057 --> 01:35:38.892
...when you get home...

873
01:35:41.062 --> 01:35:42.563
...when you get free...

874
01:35:46.069 --> 01:35:48.612
