892
01:36:50.566 --> 01:36:52.650
Take her to the closet.

893
01:36:56.865 --> 01:36:58.909
As for you...

894
01:37:01.162 --> 01:37:02.204
...it's showtime.

895
01:37:06.001 --> 01:37:07.169
[CHATTERING]

896
01:37:22.271 --> 01:37:26.150
GORSKI: The High Roller is here.
I need you to focus for me.

897
01:37:26.318 --> 01:37:28.445
Ah. Thank you.

898
01:37:30.824 --> 01:37:32.242
BLUE:
Girls?

899
01:37:32.409 --> 01:37:37.373
Can you just gather around for a second?
I wanna say a few words.

900
01:37:39.293 --> 01:37:42.337
That's all right.
You can just finish getting her dressed.

901
01:37:42.964 --> 01:37:45.258
Okay. There we go.

902
01:37:45.425 --> 01:37:47.260
BLUE:
Very nice.

903
01:37:48.972 --> 01:37:50.556
All right.

904
01:37:53.060 --> 01:37:56.939
I try to give you all...

905
01:37:57.607 --> 01:37:59.233
...a good life.

906
01:38:00.152 --> 01:38:02.612
I try. I do.

907
01:38:03.574 --> 01:38:07.243
And all I ask for in return is just for...

908
01:38:07.745 --> 01:38:09.413
...respect...

909
01:38:10.081 --> 01:38:12.125
...honesty.

910
01:38:12.293 --> 01:38:14.043
You know... Oh, that's okay, Margaret.

911
01:38:14.211 --> 01:38:17.131
A give-and-take relationship.

912
01:38:17.757 --> 01:38:20.594
But it's come to my attention...
It's come to our attention...

913
01:38:20.761 --> 01:38:24.140
...that a few bad eggs...

914
01:38:24.308 --> 01:38:26.225
...led by one little egg in particular...

915
01:38:27.769 --> 01:38:31.523
...have spit in the face
of that generosity...

916
01:38:31.691 --> 01:38:35.445
...and are plotting against me.

917
01:38:36.239 --> 01:38:37.698
Me.

918
01:38:38.950 --> 01:38:40.201
Your father.

919
