of what it is we do here?

933
01:39:23.798 --> 01:39:28.887
I teach them to survive you.

934
01:39:31.140 --> 01:39:34.894
- All right.
- I'm sorry! I didn't mean to say anything.

935
01:39:35.062 --> 01:39:36.104
I'm sorry.

936
