944
01:39:56.463 --> 01:40:01.553
But after hearing who was involved,
frankly, it started to make sense.

945
01:40:02.138 --> 01:40:04.222
- Right here?
GORSKI: Blue.

946
01:40:06.727 --> 01:40:09.855
Uh-huh. "Map. Fire."

947
01:40:11.733 --> 01:40:16.237
Looks like that chicken was counted
a little before it hatched.

948
01:40:17.741 --> 01:40:19.992
Ain't that right, Amber?

949
01:40:23.330 --> 01:40:26.292
You have anything to say? Anything?

950
01:40:27.335 --> 01:40:30.297
Blue, we didn't... We were still...

951
01:40:30.465 --> 01:40:32.090
You know what, sweetheart?

